<center><font size=7><b>Nightmare Rally</b></font></center>
<center>Number of entries found: 6</center><p>
<center>
<table width=600>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Tips</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>If you get into a sticky situation, speed ahead with Q and press Symbol
Shift.  This gets you into hyper-supercharge mode!
 <i>(Neil Deaville in Your Sinclair issue 14)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Cheat modes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>When entering your name, type these for a BEEP to start the game on the desired
level:
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;CHEVRON
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AVENUE
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SYMBOLQ
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;EXHAUST
 <i>(Neal Deaville in Your Sinclair issue 14)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Multiface pokes</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD><table border="0">
<tr>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>DESCRIPTION</B></U></TD>
<td WIDTH="200" ALIGN="LEFT"><B><U>POKE(s)</B></U></TD>
</TR>
<tr><td>Infinite lives</td><td>25112,0:26515,182:41764,0</td></tr>
<tr><td>Infinite energy</td><td>41744,182</td></tr>
</table>
<br>

&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <i>(Gerard Sweeney in Hack Attack III)</i> 
<br>
</td></tr>
<TR><TD bgcolor="blue" background=""><font color="white"><b><i>Type-in hacks</i></b></font></td></tr>
<TR><TD>This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/SinclairUser/Issue126/Tape/">this issue of Tips Amazing</a>.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Sinclair User issue 126)</i> 

<br><hr>
This can be found in <a href="ftp://ftp.void.jump.org/pub/sinclair/magazines/YourSinclair/Issue40/Tape/">this issue of Pokes</a> in the Speedlock 1 section.
 <i>(Cover Tape in Your Sinclair issue 40)</i> 

<br><hr>
<pre>
 10 CLEAR 65533: LET t=0
 20 FOR f=23296 TO 23443
 30 READ a: POKE f,a
 40 LET t=t+(f- 23286)~a: NEXT f
 50 IF t<>l240275 THEN STOP
 60 FOR f=f TO 1e9: READ a
 70 IF a>255 THEN GO TO 10D
 80 POKE f,a
 90 LET t=t+(f- 23434)~a: NEXT f
100 IF t<>a THEN STOP
110 RANDOMIZE USR 23296
120 DATA 221,33,203,92,17
130 DATA 234,6,62,255,55
140 DATA 205,86,5,48,241
150 DATA 62,224,50,8,95
160 DATA 62,235,50,11,95
170 DATA 49,252,255,14,112
180 DATA 58,148,91,111,38
190 DATA 98,229,33,252,94
200 DATA 17,192,99,217,1
210 DATA 224,184,217,118,201
220 DATA 42,149,91,1,76
230 DATA 0,22,64,93,122
240 DATA 213,213,237,1i6,225
250 DATA 14,25,9,119,14
260 DATA 4,9,119,14,8
270 DATA 9,119,14,20,9
280 DATA 119,62,201,18,42
290 DATA 149,91,14,35,237
300 DATA 66,209,116,14,3
310 DATA 9,115,14,32,9
